text: 8S or 8-S may refer to: *Crazy Eights, a card game *Crazy 8s (band), an American band *Local on the 8s, a regularly scheduled local weather forecast segment *8S, IATA airline code for Scorpio Aviation ==See also== *8 Seconds, film about American rodeo legend Lane Frost *Crazy Eights (disambiguation) *Eights (disambiguation) *S8 (disambiguation) *8 (disambiguation) for the singular of 8s
